::Aerotaur::
       He coos at baby Elita in his arms and looks up at them.  "Oh I'm 
sorry, I didn't mean to keep you from your work.  Would you like me to watch 
your baby for you until you're done?  I'd be more than happy too."  He smiles 
down at baby Elita and tickles her stomach with his free hand.  He then looks 
up at Nightlight almost begging.
